long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enhance your YouTube research with our AI-powered extension! Ask any question about a YouTube video and receive AI-generated answers tailored to the video's specific content. Effortlessly search for keywords or phrases within videos and get clickable timestamps for each mention. You can also generate concise YouTube summaries, making it easier to grasp video content at a glance. Perfect for content creators, researchers, and AI enthusiasts looking to streamline their YouTube experience with intelligent video analysis and keyword summarisation.
